Title: Strays
Plot: During a routine bust on bangers, Vic and the Team discover a money laundering ring that reaches far and wide in the crime community.  Meanwhile, Dutch takes the chilling confession of the man who was arrested in the serial-rape case, and Danny goes undercover.
GuestStars: Clark Gregg, Natalie Zea, David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Michele Hicks, Lionel Mark Smith, Vicellous Reon Shannon, Rebecca Pidgeon, DeLane Matthews, Dominic Hoffman
